title: Spain Wins the FIBA World Cup. Plus: NBA Islands! | The Mismatch
description:
The guys discuss Spain’s victory over Argentina in the 2019 FIBA World Cup finals (0:45) before comparing their respective lists of “island” players (12:00).
Hosts: Chris Vernon, Kevin O’Connor
